These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, lacrosse, biathlon, cricket, handball
5 different games are played: whist, snooker, domino, chess, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, black, ebony, light-blue, turquise
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who likes black and the person playing backgammon##2
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Sport      | weightlifting        | lacrosse | handball     | biathlon   | cricket |
| Game   | domino     | snooker      | chess | backgammon   | whist    |
| Color   | light-blue  | black     | yellow | ebony | turquise  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

