.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, may, august, march, july
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, light-blue, ebony, green, lavender
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, daffodil, tulip, lily
 1. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is between the chinese and the person who likes lavender##2
 6. the person who growstulip is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the indian is the person who likes green##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the indian is the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday         | march | october | july    | may  | august    |
| Color   | lavender    | light-blue       | ebony      | apricot | green        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Flower     | daffodil    | azalea | lily | tulip | balloon-flower |

