.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, water, cola, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, october, march, april, august
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bolivar, swisher, davidoff, vegafina
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
10. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person drinking water is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
13. the vegafina-smoker is between the person watching superhero movies and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage         | 7up | hot-chocolate     | water   | lemonade   | cola |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Birthday   | march      | october      | april       | august       | december       |
| Cigar         | bolivar | vegafina  | davidoff    | ritmeester    | swisher        |

