.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse, sailing, swimming, weightlifting
City: new-york, liverpool, hamburg, paris, marseilles
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, bike, train, car, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person traveling to paris and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to paris is the person driving the roller##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Sport         | weightlifting | parkour    | sailing  | swimming | lacrosse   |
| City   | liverpool        | new-york    | marseilles     | hamburg     | paris    |
| Transport   | bike    | train | car | jet-ski | roller   |

