5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, havana, vegafina, davidoff
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who's sport is parkour and the fan of d&b##2
 5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| City   | new-york       | boston       | marseilles   | san-francisco      | venice    |
