 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person who likes white is between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
13. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
