 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
