.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince, vegafina, game, swisher
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, november, may, december, september
City: paris, edinburgh, nizza, miami, liverpool
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the game-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the game-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who's birthday is in may and the vegafina-smoker##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
