.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
5 different pets are kept: frog, bird, chinchilla, guinea-pig, cat
City: nizza, rome, marseilles, san-francisco, berlin
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, green, blue, white
 1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person traveling to marseilles and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the owner of the cat and the person who likes ebony##2
 7. the person who likes blue is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes green##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is the person traveling to rome##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Pet           | bird | chinchilla | guinea-pig | cat    | frog  |
| City   | san-francisco  | rome    | nizza | marseilles    | berlin |
| Color   | green  | ebony        | mauve   | blue    | white     |

