.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, indie, techno, gospel, pop
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, amaryllis, azalea, bellflower
There 5 different types of food: potato, cherry, banana, pomegranate, garlic
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating cherry is between the person who growslily and the person eating potato##2
 6. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of techno is between the person driving the airplane and the fan of pop##2
 8. the fan of indie is between the fan of gospel and the fan of r&b##2
 9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
10. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Music-Genre         | pop  | techno | gospel   | indie      | r&b |
| Flower   | lily   | azalea    | zinnia | bellflower | amaryllis      |
| Food           | banana | cherry    | potato       | pomegranate     | garlic      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

