.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
House: cottage, wooden, farmhouse, go-climbing, gothic-revival
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, skiing, soccer, weightlifting
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, canasta, scrabble, go
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the malaysian and the person playing go##2
 3. the person playing go is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the thai and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the go-climbing house is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the american is the person playing snooker##1
10. the go-climbing house is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the wooden house##1
12. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| House         | farmhouse    | gothic-revival  | wooden  | cottage      | go-climbing |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | weightlifting   | soccer | skiing | water-polo   |
| Game   | canasta | mah-jongg    | go    | scrabble       | snooker         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 